revision.text: contient This class will be unsatisfiable. This is because we have given it 2 disjoint parents, which means it could never have any instances (as nothing can be both a CheeseTopping and a VegetableTopping). NB Called ProbeInconsistentTopping in the ProtegeOWL Tutorial.{{ #viki:pageTitles=CheeseyVegetableTopping}}[http://localhost/mediawiki-1.34.1/index.php/VegetableTopping is a subclass from CheeseTopping is a subclass from VegetableTopping]
